title: Dash cam video shows Sacramento protester hit by patrol car
text:
Dash cam video shows Sacramento protester hit by patrol car 11:10am IST - 01:06 
The Sacramento County Sheriff's Department showed on Monday dash camera video from a protest on Saturday when a protester was struck by a patrol car. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
